@host = http://localhost:5001

### Health
GET {{host}}/health

### Single quote — normal area
POST {{host}}/quotes/price
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "weightKg": 3,
  "originZip": "10100",
  "destinationZip": "10200"
}

### Single quote — remote area
POST {{host}}/quotes/price
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "weightKg": 10,
  "originZip": "10100",
  "destinationZip": "95000"
}

### Bulk quote
POST {{host}}/quotes/bulk
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "items": [
    { "weightKg": 2,  "originZip": "10100", "destinationZip": "10200" },
    { "weightKg": 25, "originZip": "10100", "destinationZip": "96000" },
    { "weightKg": 8,  "originZip": "30000", "destinationZip": "50000" }
  ]
}

### Get job result (replace <jobId>)
# GET {{host}}/jobs/<jobId>
